skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: dial a seal
des:
Dial-A-Seal gives you the once-in-a-lifetime chance to chat with a scatterbrained seal in the Arctic
Seals are very cheerful, please enjoy your conversation and remember to smile when you are through.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
